casebody.data:
Donna M. Joyce v. Connecticut Bar Examining Committee (11890)

Dupont, C. J., Lavery and Heiman, Js.

Argued October 28 decision released November 23, 1993 Donna M. Joyce, pro se, the appellant (petitioner). Carolyn K. Querijero, assistant attorney general, with whom, on the brief, was Richard Blumenthal, attorney general, for the appellee (respondent). Per Curiam.

The judgment is affirmed.
